    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:1.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—",
          "en": "So I have heard. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:1.2",
          "pli": "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati indakūṭe pabbate, indakassa yakkhassa bhavane. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha on Mount Indra’s Peak, the haunt of the native spirit Indaka. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho indako yakkho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
          "en": "Then the native spirit Indaka went up to the Buddha, and addressed him in verse: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:2.1",
          "pli": "“Rūpaṃ na jīvanti vadanti buddhā, ",
          "en": "“The Buddhas say that form is not the soul. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:2.2",
          "pli": "Kathaṃ nvayaṃ vindatimaṃ sarīraṃ; ",
          "en": "Then how does this body manifest? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:2.3",
          "pli": "Kutassa aṭṭhīyakapiṇḍameti, ",
          "en": "Where do the bones and liver come from? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:2.4",
          "pli": "Kathaṃ nvayaṃ sajjati gabbharasmin”ti. ",
          "en": "And how does one cling on in the womb?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:3.1",
          "pli": "“Paṭhamaṃ kalalaṃ hoti, ",
          "en": "“First there’s a drop of coagulate; "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:3.2",
          "pli": "kalalā hoti abbudaṃ; ",
          "en": "from there a little bud appears; "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:3.3",
          "pli": "Abbudā jāyate pesi, ",
          "en": "next it becomes a piece of flesh; "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:3.4",
          "pli": "pesi nibbattatī ghano; ",
          "en": "which produces a swelling. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:3.5",
          "pli": "Ghanā pasākhā jāyanti, ",
          "en": "From that swelling the limbs appear, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:3.6",
          "pli": "kesā lomā nakhāpi ca. ",
          "en": "the head hair, body hair, and teeth. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:4.1",
          "pli": "Yañcassa bhuñjatī mātā, ",
          "en": "And whatever the mother eats—"
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:4.2",
          "pli": "annaṃ pānañca bhojanaṃ; ",
          "en": "the food and drink that she consumes—"
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:4.3",
          "pli": "Tena so tattha yāpeti, ",
          "en": "nourishes them there, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn10.1:4.4",
          "pli": "mātukucchigato naro”ti. ",
          "en": "the person in the mother’s womb.”"
        }
      ],
